XML context, if available, is: <gloss xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="ἀλγεινὸς_1663">, associated with <quote xml:lang="grc">ἄλγος</quote> , here as <emph> feeling</emph> , not as <emph>causing</emph> , it: thus only here. Analogous is <cit> <bibl n="Pind. O. 1" ref="Pind. O. 1"> Pind. <title>Ol.</title> 1.26</bibl> <quote xml:lang="grc">καθαροῦ λέβητος</quote> </cit>, the cauldron of cleansing, where Fennell cp. <cit> <bibl n="Theoc. 24" ref="Theoc. 24">Theocr. 24. 95</bibl> <quote xml:lang="grc">καθαρῷ δὲ πυρώσατε δῶμα θεείῳ</quote> </cit> . </gloss>

